    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When a 6 or higher is rolled on one of your Merit dice, you gain an additional attack that can be used on your turn when you take the Attack action. You can have a maximum number of additional attacks equal to your proficiency bonus, and you cannot gain one while at your maximum.</p><p>You may only use one additional attack per turn. This benefit lasts until you finish a short or long rest. Additionally, yourself and up to your proficiency bonus number of creatures that complete a Respite gain temporary hit points equal to half your warlord level + your Charisma modifier (minimum of 1) if this is your chosen Command Style at the end of the rest.</p>",
